    "\n",
    "## 1 Machine: Set-Up\n",
    ":::{style=\"font-size: .8em\"}\n",
    "\n",
    "- _**Hypothesis**_: The probability of winning $p$, ranging from 0 to 1, with a step of 0.01.\n",
    "- _**Prior**_: Uniform, probability of $1/101$ for each hypothesis.\n",
    "- _**Likelihood of winning**_: $p,$ directly corresponds to the hypothesis.\n",
    "- _**Likelihood of losing**_: $1-p.$\n",
    "- _**Bayesian update**_: Based on the outcome of the game, win/loss.\n",
    "- _**Posterior**_: The posterior becomes the prior for the next play."
   ]
